<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.1.3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" integrity="sha384-1BmE4kWBq78iYhFldvKuhfTAU6auU8tT94WrHftjDbrCEXSU1oBoqyl2QvZ6jIW3" crossorigin="anonymous">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Roboto:wght@300&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <title>Hero-Squad</title>
    <style>
        *,
*::before,
*::after {
margin: 0;
padding: 0;
}

html {
box-sizing: border-box;
font-size: 62.5%;
}

body {
width: 90%;
margin: auto;
background-color: rgba(146, 43, 33, 1);
color: white;
font-family: 'Roboto', sans-serif;
}

#first-head {
text-align: center;
font-size: 5rem;
}
#first-para {
text-align: center;
font-size: 2rem;
}

small {
font-size: 1.5rem;
}

div {
display: flex;
flex: 0 0 210px;
width: 100%;
justify-content: center;
gap: 1.3rem;
font-size: 1.5rem;
}

.supermanFig {
    width: 210px;
}

.post-link {
    text-align: center;
    font-size: 2rem;
    margin-top 2rem;
}

a {
text-decoration: none;
}




    </style>

</head>
<body>
<h1 class="display-1" id="first-head">Welcome to Hero Squad!</h1>
<p id="first-para">Looks like you want to build your dream hero and/or hero squad. You've come to the right place!</p>
<p class="text-center"><small>Your imagination is the only thing stopping you.</small></p>
<hr>
<div>
    <figure>
        <img src="https://i.postimg.cc/DZhLKT8x/flash.png" alt="flash" height="250" width="250" />
        <figcaption>
            <p>Name: The Flash</p>
            <p>Age: 24</p>
            <p>Superpower: Super Speed.</p>
            <p>Weakness: Cold temperatures.</p>
        </figcaption>
    </figure>
    <figure>
        <img src="https://i.postimg.cc/ZKvRjQqn/invincible.jpg" alt="invincible" height="250" width="250" />
        <figcaption>
            <p>Name: Invincible</p>
            <p>Age: 16</p>
            <p>Superpower: Super Strength, Invincible.</p>
            <p>Weakness: Extreme Cold.</p>
        </figcaption>
    </figure>
    <figure>
        <img src="https://i.postimg.cc/hGsPfW2y/ironman.jpg" alt="ironman" height="250" width="250" />
        <figcaption>
            <p>Name: Iron Man</p>
            <p>Age: 40</p>
            <p>Superpower: Ultra powerful suits.</p>
            <p>Weakness: Loss of his suits.</p>
        </figcaption>
    </figure>
    <figure class="supermanFig">
        <img src="https://i.postimg.cc/25kCp9C4/superman.jpg" alt="superman" height="250" width="250" />
        <figcaption>
            <p>Name: Superman</p>
            <p>Age: 32</p>
            <p>Superpower: Super Strength, Super Speed, Heat Vision, Ice Breath, Indestructible.</p>
            <p>Weakness: Kryptonite.</p>
        </figcaption>
    </figure>
</div>
<p class="post-link"><a href="/post">Click here</a> to create your own hero.</p>
